1976;;The Duchess and the Dirtwater Fox;;American;;Melvin Frank;;Goldie Hawn, George Segal;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Duchess_and_the_Dirtwater_Fox;;A popular dance hall girl, Duchess, joins with a gambler nicknamed the "Dirtwater Fox" on the way to Salt Lake City, Utah. Seeking refuge from a pursuing gang of outlaws, the Duchess and the Dirtwater Fox join a wagon train of Mormons. On their trip, they encounter snakes, rapids, horseback pursuits through towns, and even getting tied up by the outlaws (eventually escaping).